Tech Blog

This is a journal of tips, shortcuts and solutions related to computers and technology that I encounter in my daily life. I started writing regularly in 2004 and I guess I never stopped.

I used to host my blog at codeyarns.wordpress.com where it has 10+ million views. In 2019, I decided to move from Wordpress to my own simple static platform and this is where my blog lies right now.

Listed below are the 2300+ posts of my blog. You might find it easier to find what you want by using the search bar at the top of this page.
